casebody.data:
Eddricco Li'shaun BROWN
v.
STATE of North Carolina No. 345P17 Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 16, 2017 Eddricco Brown, for Brown, Eddrico Li'shaun. Kimberly N. Callahan, Assistant Attorney General, Robert S. Banks, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 16th of October 2017 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Mitchell County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 16th of October 2017."
